Production, imports, exports, and consumption of timber products, by major product, 1965-1999

Dataset containing statistics for various timber products. Prior to 1989, pulpwood chips are not included in total production. All units are in million cubic ft.

howard5

Format

A data frame with 56 observations of 24 variables

Source

U.S. Department of Agriculture, Forest Service(16, 69); Data may not add to totals because of rounding; Data have been revised.

Details

  • AllProducts.Prod Production for all timber products
  • AllProducts.Consump Consumption for all timber products
  • Prod.Tot Total Production for Industrial Roundwood
  • Imports.Tot Total Imports for Industrial Roundwood
  • Exports.Tot Total Exports for Industrial Roundwood
  • Consump.Tot Total Consumption for Industrial Roundwood
  • Lumber.Prod Production for Lumber Products
  • Lumber.Imports Imports for Lumber Products
  • Lumber.Exports Exports for Lumber Products
  • Lumber.Consump Consumption for Lumber Products
  • PlywoodVeneer.Prod Production for Plywood and Veneer Products
  • PlywoodVeneer.Imports Imports for Plywood and Veneer Products
  • PlywoodVeneer.Exports Exports for Plywood and Veneer Products
  • PlywoodVeneer.Consump Consumption for Plywood and Veneer Products
  • Pulpwood.Prod Production for Pulpwood Products
  • Pulpwood.Imports Imports for Pulpwood Products
  • Pulpwood.Exports Exports for Pulpwood Products
  • Pulpwood.Consump Consumption for Pulpwood Products
  • OtherIndProductsandConsump Other Industrial Products, production and consumption.
  • Logs.Imports Log Imports
  • Logs.Exports Log Exports
  • PulpwoodChip.Imports Pulpwood chip Imports
  • PulpwoodChip.Exports Pulpwood chip Exports
  • FuelwoodProdandConsump Fuelwood production and consumption
